id: pm-0xhj
title: Context blocked-fallback test uses date-sensitive default deadline
description: "The context blocked-fallback unit test used a helper default +1d deadline for a draft seed, making coverage fail when +1d lands inside the explicit agenda window."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[6]: audit,calendar,context,dogfood,pm-cli,tests
created_at: "2026-04-30T19:53:17.267Z"
updated_at: "2026-04-30T20:03:58.567Z"
deadline: "2026-05-01T19:53:17.267Z"
author: codex-audit
estimated_minutes: 20
acceptance_criteria: Context blocked-fallback test uses deterministic absolute seed dates and coverage no longer fails on the current date.
parent: pm-3fti
resolution: Made the draft seed deadline explicit and outside the May 1 context agenda window.
expected_result: The blocked-fallback context test has one deterministic agenda event regardless of current date.
actual_result: Targeted context test passed through both direct run and pm linked-test execution.
fixed_version: 2026.3.12-audit
