close_reason: Context blocked-fallback seed is date-stable; linked pm test passed.
body: "Coverage finding: on 2026-04-30, the draft seed in tests/unit/context-command.spec.ts resolved its default +1d deadline to 2026-05-01, inside the test window. The agenda then had two non-terminal events instead of the expected one blocked deadline."
